{"tid":2234932,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"彭斯白頭髮配黑蒼蠅圖爆紅 拜登陣營推出產品：真相蒼蠅拍","createTime":"2020-10-08T09:08:59.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-08T09:10:12.000Z","uid":28765,"like":1,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"7dd5a377a4c0378b8503780eb564d33b872fc726","tid":2234932,"uid":28765,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-08T09:08:59.000Z","msg":"〔即時新聞／綜合報導〕今日舉行的美國副總統大選辯論會中發生有趣小插曲，一隻黑色蒼蠅停在共和黨副總統候選人彭斯的白頭髮上，意外顯眼，也引發社群平台網友熱議。而對手拜登陣營也打趣在官網推出「誠實蒼蠅拍產品」，再度掀起討論。<br />\n<br />\n&middot;&middot;&middot;&middot;&middot;<br />\n<br />\n另外，民主黨總統參選人拜登的官網也立刻推出「真相蒼蠅拍」（Truth Over Flies Fly Swatter），一支販售10美元（約新台幣285元）<br />\n<br />\n&middot;&middot;&middot;&middot;&middot;<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/3315602\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F3315602&d=xM4HlgsByf6UCiwKp%2FWW5LTr7UizNwCuyTydxCoZ6r4%3D&h=4b1be948\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F3315602&h=321066d8\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/3315602</a>"},{"pid":"a402b001513d83f5f59b36c18d0a7cb48d4bc0de","tid":2234932,"uid":135740,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-08T09:10:12.000Z","msg":"on9當有趣"}]}